{"tid":880323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"難以置信，香港地竟然仲有人無payme","createTime":"2018-10-28T15:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T16:00:16.000Z","uid":84102,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c4e4bfc518130e965adcf9ba808bed4b7e7790","tid":880323,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"今日同班FD子出去食飯吹水<br />\n食到差唔多埋單嘅時候<br />\n竟然其中有一個毒撚無啦啦講幾多錢呀 我得大紙同少少散紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係即場笑左出黎  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我 : 乜你冇Payme架咩？ 我俾住先你過返俾我囉<br />\n佢 : 吓無呀 我爭住你幾蚊先啦 <br />\n我 : 你講笑咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n之後見個毒撚係度巢褲袋打算俾啲散銀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係掛 竟然仲有人無payme <br />\n咩人黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac9491efbe52df5fe1076aa66484369d9ef72fc","tid":880323,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}